Enkomono te nkaraki eretoto


1  Woi iyie ora olainyalani, leton eitu kinyali iyie, niaata enkeleekisho, neitu iyie kintaasi embae e nkeleekisho! Ore ake pee indip ainyalisho nikinyali sii ninye iyie; ore pee indip mbaa inono e nkeleekisho nikintaasi iyie inenkeleekisho. 
2  Olaitoriani ing'urrie iyiook, iyie iyiook kiaanyita. Taa enkaina ang anaake tadekenya, neaku enjeunoto ang te nkata e nyamali. 
3  Ore to ltoilo le ndarata neisik iltung'ana, ore ti nidumunye iyie neidapasha loreren. 
4  Naa kearari intokitin inono neishunye anaa enaishu oimaat enkop; anaa enaitiam olmaati te nkop, neitiam iltung'ana te nkop. 
5  Keisisi Olaitoriani, amu etii ninye shumata oleng; keiput ninye Sion esipata o esupatisho. 
6  Naa ninye olo aaku enkitashoto too nkatitin inyi, neaku kitok enjeunoto, o eng'eno o eyiolounoto; naa euriata o Laitoriani ninye olchumati lenye. 
7  Ng'ura lelo oing'ok, eishirita ninche ti auluo; ore lelo balusuni le seriani, neishirita te mion. 
8  Etoliyiote nkoitoi sapuki meekure eetae olalotoni. Etigile olning'o, netemenayioki ilchakenini, meetae oltung'ani oshilaa olikae. 
9  Eishirita enkop netalepori to sina; etumute Lebanon netoyio; etotiuo Sharon anaa olpurkel; ore Bashan o Karmel neipiripiroitie mbenek enye.

Eikoo Olaitoriani to lmang'ati lenyena


10  “Kadumunye nanu taata,” Olaitoriani ojo, “Ore taata kaitashe nanu; naa kaayiolouni nanu taata. 
11  Ntobiribiri intae mbaa naaijo suut, nipuopuo aayau mbaa e pesho; ore enkiyang'et inyi naa enkima namut intae. 
12  Netiu olorere anaa ilootapejoyioki aaitaa enkuruoni, netiu anaa ilkiku ootudung'oki nepejori te nkima.” 
13  Entoning intae lelo oolakua, ina nataasa nanu; ore intae kulo oolakua, entayiolo enkidimata ai. 
14  Ore lelo aing'okok ootii Sion neiruto; eibung'a olokirikiri lelo lemeyiolo Enkai: “Kalo ti atua iyiook oidim atotona te nkima nanyaisho? Kalo ti atua iyiook oidim atobiko te nkima oo ntarasi?” 
15  Ore ilo olo too nkoitoi naaitoriori neiro sipat, ilo omenaa tumoto e nkitorogonyare, ilo oipirripir nkaik enyena meibung ntokitin e ropare, ilo oiken nkiyiaa enyena pee mening enkibukoroto o sarge; neiken nkonyek enyena pee meing'or entorroni. 
16  Ilo ninye olo aton too wuejiitin e shumata; ore ewueji e nkirrita naa isempewueti too soito; nepuoi aaisho ninye endaa o enkare.

Mbaa enking'asia naayooki aapuonu


17  Keyooki nkonyek inono aaing'or olaiguanani te nkishiaa enye; neing'or ninche aaing'or ina kop dapash oleng. 
18  Nepuo indamunot inyi aaing'asia te ilo kirutoto, nijojo, “Koree ninye ilo apa oikenisho, Koree ninye ilo apa oineneng atem kodi? Koree ninye ilo apa oiken iltaleta?” 
19  Mingiligili ae kata aadol lelo tung'ana leeiking'a, lelo tung'ana limiyiololo intae enkutuk enye nimindimidimi aatoning'u ooiramiram te nkutuk nimining'ung'u. 
20  Eng'ura Sion, ina anasa gelunoti nikipolosishore iyiook! Kepuo nkonyek inono aadol Yerusalem, ina manyisho naitirring'a, ilo ng'obor lemeigusugus, lemedotunye ae kata nena sheito naaunore, nemedung'o nena keenta naaenare. 
21  Ore te ine nelo Olaitoriani te nkitoo aaku te nebo iyiook ewueji ine netii ilkejek dapashi o erat, nemeim ine imelin e enkitoo. 
22  Amu Olaitoriani ninye olarishani lang Olaitoriani ninye olo aitore iyiook, Olaitoriani ninye olaiguanani lang; keitajeu ninye iyiook. 
23  Eitololong'ita nkeenta e meli; meitirrishayu ninche. Ore nena masaa kumok neori keyae o mewaita ilmaiman. 
24  Nemeetae obo omanya ina kop ojo, “Kamuei nanu”; ore lelo tung'ana oomanya ine naa kepalakini ing'ok enye.

